{"tid":382361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人在日本有無巴絲要幫手買IQOS/GLO？","createTime":"2017-08-31T15:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T02:25:37.000Z","uid":6847,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c215d2b26019380891fdf4e14caa8728e32522d1","tid":382361,"uid":6847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"人在日本 強烈推薦轉會食GLO 堅好過1QOS<br />\n要幫手買的請PM<br />\n注意！我只係順手買！唔係代購同農夫<br />\n食後感<br />\n岩岩試完呢個GLO<br />\n反而認為比IQOS好比較貼近真煙火口感<br />\n因為GLO係成支煙加熱（可以睇圖3）<br />\nIQOS只係加熱一點<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/234410_3f8bc6c5c5f50418e4c5222f068e386f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F234410_3f8bc6c5c5f50418e4c5222f068e386f.jpg&h=e3dc67c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/234411_6e4355f95e899538b434b50559f2888f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F234411_6e4355f95e899538b434b50559f2888f.jpg&h=caf6d2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/234412_a3262e46361b5c6af62dd0cb0ceb8999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F234412_a3262e46361b5c6af62dd0cb0ceb8999.jpg&h=febf28f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但GLO其實唔係太大<br />\nGLO其實好細個食完<br />\n可以馬上食第2支唔洗等開關機都會有震動"},{"pid":"294eebecee4e6aef07f45465baab75eb13c07953","tid":382361,"uid":6847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fcfad6729b9d340a2a4f68a02525300c554eef","tid":382361,"uid":42895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:32:23.000Z","msg":"有興趣 Glo<br />\n留tg?"},{"pid":"d56bdc013289ae4b05c979cc2e3c248dfdcae16b","tid":382361,"uid":87674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09